[sysdig_secure_vulnerabilities://<name>]
sysdig_secure_url = Enter your Sysdig Secure URL for your Sysdig region (https must be included)Examples: https://secure.sysdig.com, https://us2.app.sysdig.com, https://eu1.app.sysdig.com, ...
sysdig_secure_token = Enter your Sysdig Secure API Token
nvd_api_key = Provide a NVD API Key (see https://nvd.nist.gov/developers/request-an-api-key) to retrieve vulnerability descriptions.
vulnerability_details = Choose the vulnerability details included as part of the event. If Vulnerability Description is selected, it is strongly encouraged to provide a NVD API Key to avoid hitting the rate limit.
max_images = Maximum number of images to retrieve, for testing purposes